trans-unit.source: Using the QuickBooks Migration Extension | Microsoft Docs

seg-source.mrk: Using the QuickBooks Migration Extension | Microsoft Docs

target.mrk: Použití rozšíření QuickBooks Migration | Microsoft Docs

trans-unit.source: Describes how to use the extension to migrate customers, vendors, items, and accounts from QuickBooks Online to Business Central.

seg-source.mrk: Describes how to use the extension to migrate customers, vendors, items, and accounts from QuickBooks Online to Business Central.

target.mrk: Popisuje, jak používat rozšíření k migraci zákazníků, dodavatelů, zboží a účtů z QuickBooks Online do Business Central.

trans-unit.source: The QuickBooks Online Data Migration Extension

seg-source.mrk: The QuickBooks Online Data Migration Extension

target.mrk: Rozšíření QuickBooks Online Data Migration

trans-unit.source: This extension is included in the **Data Migration** assisted setup guide to help you migrate important business data from QuickBooks Online to [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)].

seg-source.mrk: This extension is included in the **Data Migration** assisted setup guide to help you migrate important business data from QuickBooks Online to [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)].

target.mrk: Toto rozšíření je zahrnuto v Průvodci asistovaného nastavení **migrace dat**, který vám pomůže při migraci důležitých obchodních dat z QuickBooks Online do [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)].

trans-unit.source: For example, this is useful when your business is growing, and you've decided to upgrade your business management app by starting to use [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)].

seg-source.mrk: For example, this is useful when your business is growing, and you've decided to upgrade your business management app by starting to use [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)].

target.mrk: To je užitečné například v době, kdy vaše firma roste, a tak jste se rozhodli upgradovat aplikaci pro správu firmy a začali jste používat [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)].

trans-unit.source: Open documents for customers and vendors, such as invoices, credit memos, and payments

seg-source.mrk: Open documents for customers and vendors, such as invoices, credit memos, and payments

target.mrk: Otevřené dokumenty pro zákazníky a dodavatele, jako faktury, dobropisy a platby

trans-unit.source: We migrate only full amounts on sales and purchase documents.

seg-source.mrk: We migrate only full amounts on sales and purchase documents.

target.mrk: Migrujeme pouze plnou částku v prodejních a nákupních fakturách.

trans-unit.source: We do not update partially paid amounts.

seg-source.mrk: We do not update partially paid amounts.

target.mrk: Neaktualizujeme částečně zaplacené částky.

trans-unit.source: For example, if a customer has paid 300 of a total of 500 dollars on a sales invoice, we migrate the full 500.

seg-source.mrk: For example, if a customer has paid 300 of a total of 500 dollars on a sales invoice, we migrate the full 500.

target.mrk: Například, jestliže zákazník zaplatil 300, z celkových 500 korun na prodejní faktuře, migrujeme celých 500.

trans-unit.source: If you have received partial payments, you must update these manually, either before or after you migrate data.

seg-source.mrk: If you have received partial payments, you must update these manually, either before or after you migrate data.

target.mrk: Jestli jste obdrželi částečnou platbu, tak ji musíte aktualizovat manuálně, buď před, nebo po migraci dat.

trans-unit.source: We recommend that you apply outstanding transactions before you migrate, just to make things easier afterward.

seg-source.mrk: We recommend that you apply outstanding transactions before you migrate, just to make things easier afterward.

target.mrk: Doporučujeme abyste před migrací použili neuhrazené transakce, aby bylo možné později věci zjednodušit.

trans-unit.source: We do not migrate purchase orders or sales orders.

seg-source.mrk: We do not migrate purchase orders or sales orders.

target.mrk: Nemigrujeme nákupní a prodejní objednávky.

trans-unit.source: Before you start

seg-source.mrk: Before you start

target.mrk: Než začnete

trans-unit.source: An important part of the migration process is to specify the accounts to migrate transactions to.

seg-source.mrk: An important part of the migration process is to specify the accounts to migrate transactions to.

target.mrk: Důležitá část migračního procesu je specifikovat účty, do kterých budou transakce migrovat.

trans-unit.source: It's a good idea to plan this mapping before you migrate data.

seg-source.mrk: It's a good idea to plan this mapping before you migrate data.

target.mrk: Je dobrý nápad si toto mapování naplánovat před migrací dat.

trans-unit.source: For example, the accounts where you post transactions for:

seg-source.mrk: For example, the accounts where you post transactions for:

target.mrk: Například, účty, ve kterých zúčtujete transakce pro:

trans-unit.source: The sale of items or services to customers.

seg-source.mrk: The sale of items or services to customers.

target.mrk: Prodej zboží a služeb odběratelům.

trans-unit.source: The purchase of items or services from vendors.

seg-source.mrk: The purchase of items or services from vendors.

target.mrk: Nákup zboží a služeb od dodavatelů.

trans-unit.source: Adjustments in the general ledger.

seg-source.mrk: Adjustments in the general ledger.

target.mrk: Opravné položky v hlavní knize.

trans-unit.source: [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)] requires that general ledger accounts have account numbers assigned to them.

seg-source.mrk: requires that general ledger accounts have account numbers assigned to them.

target.mrk: vyžaduje, aby měly účty v hlavní knize přiřazené čísla účtů.

trans-unit.source: Make sure that account numbers are assigned to your accounts in QuickBooks Online.

seg-source.mrk: Make sure that account numbers are assigned to your accounts in QuickBooks Online.

target.mrk: Ujistěte se, že čísla účtů jsou přiřazená k vašim účtům v QuickBooks Online.

trans-unit.source: If transactions in QuickBooks Online have tax amounts, you must set up a tax account for your tax jurisdictions in [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)] before you can post transactions.

seg-source.mrk: If transactions in QuickBooks Online have tax amounts, you must set up a tax account for your tax jurisdictions in [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)] before you can post transactions.

target.mrk: Pokud mají transakce v aplikaci QuickBooks Online daňové částky, musíte před zaúčtováním transakcí vytvořit daňový účet pro vaše daňové kompetence v aplikaci [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)].

trans-unit.source: How do I start using the extension?

seg-source.mrk: How do I start using the extension?

target.mrk: Jak začnu používat rozšíření?

trans-unit.source: Getting started is easy.

seg-source.mrk: Getting started is easy.

target.mrk: Začít je snadné.

trans-unit.source: All you need to do is run the **Data Migration** assisted setup guide.

seg-source.mrk: All you need to do is run the **Data Migration** assisted setup guide.

target.mrk: Stačí spustit Průvodce asistovaného nastavení **migrace dat**.

trans-unit.source: Here's how:

seg-source.mrk: Here's how:

target.mrk: Zde je návod:

trans-unit.source: Choose the ![Lightbulb that opens the Tell Me feature](media/ui-search/search_small.png "Tell me what you want to do") icon, enter **Assisted Setup**, and then choose **Migrate business data**.

seg-source.mrk: Choose the ![Lightbulb that opens the Tell Me feature](media/ui-search/search_small.png "Tell me what you want to do") icon, enter **Assisted Setup**, and then choose **Migrate business data**.

target.mrk: Vyberte ![Žárovku, která otevře ikonu funkce Řekněte mi](media/ui-search/search_small.png "Řekněte mi, co chcete dělat"), zadejte ** Asistovaná nastavení ** a poté vyberte **Migrovat obchodní data**.

trans-unit.source: Follow the instructions on each step in the assisted setup guide.

seg-source.mrk: Follow the instructions on each step in the assisted setup guide.

target.mrk: Postupujte podle instrukcí k jednotlivým krokům v asistovaném průvodci nastavením.

trans-unit.source: What do I do after I migrate data?

seg-source.mrk: What do I do after I migrate data?

target.mrk: Co mám dělat po migraci dat?

trans-unit.source: After you migrate data, transactions have the status **Unposted**, so you can review them and make adjustments.

seg-source.mrk: After you migrate data, transactions have the status **Unposted**, so you can review them and make adjustments.

target.mrk: Po migraci dat mají transakce stav **Nezveřejněno**, takže je můžete zkontrolovat a provést úpravy.

trans-unit.source: To review the transactions, go to the page where you would normally find them.

seg-source.mrk: To review the transactions, go to the page where you would normally find them.

target.mrk: Pokud chcete transakce zkontrolovat, přejděte na stránku, kde je obvykle najdete.

trans-unit.source: For example, to review unposted sales invoices, go to the **Sales Invoices** page.

seg-source.mrk: For example, to review unposted sales invoices, go to the **Sales Invoices** page.

target.mrk: Chcete-li například zkontrolovat nezveřejněné prodejní faktury, přejděte na stránku **Prodejní faktury**.

trans-unit.source: To review payment journals, go to the **Payment Journals** page.

seg-source.mrk: To review payment journals, go to the **Payment Journals** page.

target.mrk: Jestli chcete zkontrolovat deníky plateb, přejděte na stránku **Deníky plateb**.

trans-unit.source: There are a few things in particular that you should do:

seg-source.mrk: There are a few things in particular that you should do:

target.mrk: Je zde několik věcí, které by jste měli zejména udělat:

trans-unit.source: If the transactions in QuickBooks Online had markup or discount amounts, you must manually add the amounts to the related transactions in [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)] before you post them.

seg-source.mrk: If the transactions in QuickBooks Online had markup or discount amounts, you must manually add the amounts to the related transactions in [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)] before you post them.

target.mrk: Pokud transakce v aplikaci QuickBooks Online měly přirážku, nebo slevu, musíte je před zaúčtováním manuálně přidat do souvisejících transakcí v [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)].

trans-unit.source: If you are using value added tax (VAT), you may need to add a business posting group and a product posting group to the posting setup so that you can post VAT amounts.

seg-source.mrk: If you are using value added tax (VAT), you may need to add a business posting group and a product posting group to the posting setup so that you can post VAT amounts.

target.mrk: Pokud jste plátci DPH, budete možná muset do nastavení účtování přidat Obchodní účetní skupinu a Účetní skupinu zboží, abyste mohli účtovat DPH.

trans-unit.source: Verify the beginning balances for accounts in the general ledger.

seg-source.mrk: Verify the beginning balances for accounts in the general ledger.

target.mrk: Ověřte počáteční stavy pro účty v hlavní knize.

trans-unit.source: QuickBooks Online does not store the current balance for all accounts, so you might need to correct beginning balances.

seg-source.mrk: QuickBooks Online does not store the current balance for all accounts, so you might need to correct beginning balances.

target.mrk: QuickBooks Online neukládá aktuální stavy všech účtů, takže budete pravděpodobně muset opravit počáteční stavy.
